  cat <<EOF
Usage:
  kite test [options] [target-directory]

Detect project stack, resolve the configured verification profile, and run the matching test tiers.

Options:
  --tier T            Run a specific tier: unit, integration, e2e, a11y, perf, security
                      Repeatable. Use --tier all for the full matrix.
  --profile P         Expand a saved profile: smoke, standard, or full
  --e2e               Backward-compatible alias for --tier e2e
  -h, --help           Show this help text

Monorepo support:
  Automatically discovers root projects, common app folders, package-manager
